gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Lord Prithu Rishabhadew Rajan, Hayagreev Hari Dharit tan;
Hams Murti Dhavantari, Avyaa Vyasa Narad Tan Dharie.

Here is the translation:

This way is uncertain, it will happen with Parvatabhai's permission; 
That is what I said once, there are many like those and many more.

Here is the translation:

When you test, test with great effort, no one will take it easily; 
Later, I thought in my mind, the power of God's arrangement became clear.
